nvolving Iranian missile barrages and Israeli strikes on Iranian targets, have disrupted regional stability and rattled global energy markets, with Iraq and Syria closing airspace.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/stop-shooting-donald-trump-demands-as-iran-israel-resume-strikes-1st-time-post-april-ceasefire/articleshow/131583880.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/stop-shooting-donald-trump-demands-as-iran-israel-resume-strikes-1st-time-post-april-ceasefire/articleshow/131583880.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T15:34:11+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Yashasvi Vasistha</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131584903,imgsize-52154.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[24 Indian seafarers seek urgent help after vessel reportedly attacked off Oman coast]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131584590.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Twenty-four Indian seafarers are urgently seeking help after their vessel was reportedly attacked off Oman's coast, near the Strait of Hormuz. The Forward Seamen's Union of India has appealed to the Indian Navy and authorities for intervention amidst rising regional tensions. Details regarding the attack and the vessel remain unconfirmed by official sources.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/24-indian-seafarers-seek-urgent-help-after-vessel-reportedly-attacked-off-oman-coast/articleshow/131584590.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/24-indian-seafarers-seek-urgent-help-after-vessel-reportedly-attacked-off-oman-coast/articleshow/131584590.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T15:24:37+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Ayush Pandey</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131584705,imgsize-37902.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UAE grants 3-day weekend to students, private sector and government employees for Islamic New Year]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131583610.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[UAE residents will enjoy a public holiday on Monday, June 15, 2026, for the Islamic New Year. This official break, announced by FAHR and MoHRE, grants both public and private sector employees a three-day weekend. Schools and educational institutions will also observe the holiday, with normal operations resuming Tuesday.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-grants-3-day-weekend-to-students-private-sector-and-government-employees-for-islamic-new-year/articleshow/131583610.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-grants-3-day-weekend-to-students-private-sector-and-government-employees-for-islamic-new-year/articleshow/131583610.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T15:08:47+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131584262,imgsize-61410.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[The 400-year-old ocean secret that protected fish long before modern conservation existed]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131583839.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/the-400-year-old-ocean-secret-that-protected-fish-long-before-modern-conservation-existed/articleshow/131583839.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/the-400-year-old-ocean-secret-that-protected-fish-long-before-modern