ther-rain-clears-but-cooler-showery-conditions-set-to-continue-this-week/articleshow/131581639.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-weather-rain-clears-but-cooler-showery-conditions-set-to-continue-this-week/articleshow/131581639.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T13:04:52+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131581658,imgsize-143746.cms"/></item></channel></rss>